Company Overview of Jefferies LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Jefferies LLC provides investment banking, sales, trading, and research and strategy across the spectrum of equities, fixed income, foreign exchange, futures, commodities, and wealth management to investors, companies, and government entities in the Americas, Europe, and the Middle East and Asia. Its investment banking products include debt capital markets, equity capital markets, mergers and acquisitions, restructuring and recapitalization, and U.K. corporate broking. The company provides sales, trading, and capital markets platforms for cash equities, electronic trading solutions, equity derivatives, convertibles, prime services, and corporate access; and for fixed income products. It deli...
Jefferies LLC provides investment banking, sales, trading, and research and strategy across the spectrum of equities, fixed income, foreign exchange, futures, commodities, and wealth management to investors, companies, and government entities in the Americas, Europe, and the Middle East and Asia. Its investment banking products include debt capital markets, equity capital markets, mergers and acquisitions, restructuring and recapitalization, and U.K. corporate broking. The company provides sales, trading, and capital markets platforms for cash equities, electronic trading solutions, equity derivatives, convertibles, prime services, and corporate access; and for fixed income products. It delivers execution, clearing, and customizable technology solutions to trade base and ferrous metals, precious metals, foreign exchange, and exchange-traded futures and options. The company provides research and strategy to offer insights and actionable ideas on strategy and economics, equity, fixed income, foreign exchange, and commodities. It provides asset management programs for convertible bonds, quantitative strategies, and long-short equities to private investment funds; separate accounts. The company also provides wealth management services, such as portfolio management services, executive services, and family office services to high-net-worth individuals, family offices, and others. It caters to consumer and retail; energy; financial institutions; financial sponsors; healthcare; industrials; media and telecom; public finance; real estate, gaming and lodging; and technology sectors. The company was formerly known as Jefferies & Company, Inc. and changed its name to Jefferies LLC in March 2013. The company was founded in 1962 and is based in New York, New York with additional offices in Beijing, Shanghai, China; Toronto; Canada; and United States. Jefferies LLC operates as a subsidiary of Jefferies Group LLC.
Detailed Description


