Samson Resources II To Market Its Assets In East Texas And North Louisiana
May 8 17
Samson Resources II, LLC announced that following a strategic review of its core competencies and underlying reserve and production potential conducted by Jefferies LLC and Houlihan Lokey Capital, Inc., Samson Resources has decided to market for sale its assets in East Texas and North Louisiana through a broad marketing process to be conducted by Jefferies and Houlihan Lokey.


